1
00:01:00,479 --> 00:01:01,560
What are you spacing out for?

2
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:06,200
Don't tell me every time I pass out,

3
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:09,000
that's when it's the real deal?

4
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:10,640
Well, you can't really say that.

5
00:01:10,799 --> 00:01:12,719
But you did pass out back in Yunling.

6
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:14,760
Every time you held this pearl,

7
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:15,879
your face would twist up,

8
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:17,280
all kinds of messed up.

9
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:19,159
This time you're so calm,

10
00:01:19,799 --> 00:01:23,079
means this divine pearl has no real magic.

11
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,000
Bro,

12
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:26,599
how about we take this pearl abroad?

13
00:01:26,599 --> 00:01:27,879
The archaeology department at my school

14
00:01:27,879 --> 00:01:30,079
has a team studying mysterious antiques like this.

15
00:01:30,799 --> 00:01:32,000
No way.

16
00:01:32,079 --> 00:01:33,560
This belongs to China.

17
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:34,879
How can it go abroad?

18
00:01:34,879 --> 00:01:36,319
That'd be smuggling national treasures.

19
00:01:43,879 --> 00:01:44,680
We're so busy celebrating,

20
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:45,239
we forgot

21
00:01:45,519 --> 00:01:46,760
we're sitting on a volcano!

22
00:01:47,239 --> 00:01:48,200
We've got the pearl anyway,

23
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,000
so let's get out of here.

24
00:01:49,079 --> 00:01:49,879
Yes, yes, yes.

25
00:01:53,599 --> 00:01:54,280
Oh no.

26
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:55,640
Look at that.

27
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:56,439
This...

28
00:01:57,239 --> 00:01:58,200
What is it? What's wrong?

29
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,239
What are you looking at?

30
00:01:59,239 --> 00:02:02,000
The tree sap melted and sealed the exit.

31
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:03,760
Run!

32
00:02:03,959 --> 00:02:04,719
Go, go, go! Hurry!

33
00:02:04,719 --> 00:02:05,560
Quick, quick, quick!

34
00:02:05,879 --> 00:02:06,400
Move it!

35
00:02:07,359 --> 00:02:08,319
Come on!

36
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:09,159
You go first.

37
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,120
Okay, okay, okay.

38
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:14,919
Fatty!

39
00:02:16,919 --> 00:02:17,479
What is it?

40
00:02:19,199 --> 00:02:19,639
Nothing.

41
00:02:20,319 --> 00:02:21,479
Quit freaking me out.

42
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:40,560
Hey,

43
00:02:40,719 --> 00:02:42,280
did you know I'd step right into this?

44
00:02:42,879 --> 00:02:43,680
It's so sticky.

45
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:46,120
Let's get out first. Move!

46
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:47,919
So weird.

47
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:58,319
Old Lu!

48
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:00,759
Bro!

49
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,199
The ground's splitting open!

50
00:03:02,639 --> 00:03:03,840
I can see the lava!

51
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,400
Fatty,

52
00:03:11,319 --> 00:03:12,120
get everyone out first.

53
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:12,759
Got it.

54
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:20,080
Stay behind me.

55
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:33,319
A brush with death.

56
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:34,599
You can say that again.

57
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:36,120
I just don't know

58
00:03:36,439 --> 00:03:37,199
if this Lingxiao Pearl

59
00:03:37,199 --> 00:03:39,319
can lift the curse on Old Chen.

60
00:03:39,319 --> 00:03:40,439
Do you still remember

61
00:03:40,719 --> 00:03:41,560
the murals in the tomb passage?

62
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:43,240
Are you saying the dates on the murals

63
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,840
match the dates of crustal movement?

64
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,159
Exactly.

65
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,560
The Dian King was waiting for his chance to Become immortal,

66
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,360
but for the Sacrificial Ritual,

67
00:03:51,879 --> 00:03:53,120
besides the Lingxiao Pearl,

68
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,560
he also needed a Natural Portent.

69
00:03:55,159 --> 00:03:56,400
In modern terms,

70
00:03:56,719 --> 00:03:57,840
that means a volcanic eruption.

71
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,199
Gu Valley recorded several times before,

72
00:03:59,199 --> 00:04:00,360
but they were just tectonic shifts.

73
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,680
The lava never erupted.

74
00:04:01,759 --> 00:04:02,439
That's why they

75
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:03,879
kept passing this message down,

76
00:04:03,879 --> 00:04:05,719
until the day the volcano truly erupts,

77
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:07,159
so descendants could use the Lingxiao Pearl

78
00:04:07,159 --> 00:04:08,439
to complete the Sacrificial Ritual.

79
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,240
Then isn't this the perfect timing?

80
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,080
If by any chance

81
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:13,120
it can lift the curse on Old Chen,

82
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,879
wouldn't that be a win-win?

83
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,279
Exactly.

84
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,000
Wait, isn't that...

85
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,480
Isn't that the altar right there?

86
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,720
Let's go check it out.

87
00:04:23,079 --> 00:04:24,360
Got eagle eyes, huh?

88
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,399
Let's go.

89
00:04:34,639 --> 00:04:35,639
We need to pick up the pace.

90
00:04:35,639 --> 00:04:36,759
This ground's about to crack open.

91
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:37,560
What?

92
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,240
Hurry!

93
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:43,600
You're just being alarmist. Where's the...

94
00:04:48,879 --> 00:04:49,600
Commander Chen,

95
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,279
you've got the gift of foresight!

96
00:04:52,279 --> 00:04:53,279
Enough, quit yapping.

97
00:04:53,879 --> 00:04:55,319
There'll be bigger cracks up ahead soon.

98
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,399
Get moving.

99
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:59,600
Quick! Listen to Commander Chen!

100
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,439
Move, move!

101
00:05:07,959 --> 00:05:08,560
Fatty,

102
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,279
have I ever told you

103
00:05:10,399 --> 00:05:12,920
you're the most agile fat guy I've ever seen?

104
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:13,959
Do you even need to ask?

105
00:05:13,959 --> 00:05:15,160
Fatty has always been.

106
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:16,600
Old Chen, hurry over!

107
00:05:16,879 --> 00:05:17,319
Fatty,

108
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:18,759
catch my bag!

109
00:05:18,759 --> 00:05:19,600
Bro, wait a sec.

110
00:05:20,759 --> 00:05:21,319
What's wrong?

111
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:23,800
If you throw this bag over,

112
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,519
what if it accidentally falls down?

113
00:05:26,639 --> 00:05:28,160
You care that much about my bag?

114
00:05:29,079 --> 00:05:30,360
The Lingxiao Pearl is in the bag!

115
00:05:30,639 --> 00:05:32,519
Haven't we come all this way for it?

116
00:05:32,519 --> 00:05:33,519
If it falls down,

117
00:05:33,639 --> 00:05:35,519
wouldn't all our efforts be wasted?

118
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:38,040
Right, right, that makes sense.

119
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:41,920
I forgot to ask you,

120
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,439
didn't you come to catch butterflies?

121
00:05:43,439 --> 00:05:44,839
Not fulfilling your dad's last wish,

122
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:46,079
isn't it a big regret?

123
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,439
Although I didn't find

124
00:05:48,439 --> 00:05:49,639
the Kashenfu Ghost Beauty Butterfly,

125
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:51,639
I photographed many other butterflies.

126
00:05:51,839 --> 00:05:53,439
After I go back and develop them,

127
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:54,439
I'll mail them to you right away.

128
00:05:54,439 --> 00:05:55,439
Old Chen, come on over!

129
00:05:56,639 --> 00:05:57,360
Ding Dawei.

130
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,160
Your dad passed away, right?

131
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,759
What about your mom?

132
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:07,000
My mom passed away too.

133
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:09,480
Why are you still walking in circles?

134
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:11,279
Hurry up, or you'll get burned soon.

135
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:15,639
Everyone,

136
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:17,959
I've made a decision.

137
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,120
This Lingxiao Pearl,

138
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,439
I don't want it anymore.

139
00:06:22,639 --> 00:06:23,439
Don't say that.

140
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,279
Old Chen, are you crazy?

141
00:06:26,319 --> 00:06:27,879
This is a cultural relic!

142
00:06:27,879 --> 00:06:29,720
Haven't you been guarding it with your life?

143
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,160
Exactly.

144
00:06:31,279 --> 00:06:32,079
Hey, Commander Chen,

145
00:06:32,079 --> 00:06:34,600
don't you want to lift that curse of yours?

146
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:35,680
This Lingxiao Pearl

147
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,439
has nothing to do with my curse.

148
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:39,000
You haven't even tried.

149
00:06:39,319 --> 00:06:40,600
How do you know it's unrelated?

150
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:43,279
Shutong, I promise you.

151
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,560
Please trust me.

152
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:46,360
Once we get out of here,

153
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,560
I'll go abroad with you for treatment.

154
00:06:48,639 --> 00:06:50,160
When I touched the Lingxiao Pearl just now,

155
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,319
I got a really bad feeling.

156
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,519
It's going to bring us danger.

157
00:06:54,839 --> 00:06:55,800
It's not dangerous.

158
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:57,439
Chen Youxi,

159
00:06:58,519 --> 00:07:01,439
what did you feel when you touched the Lingxiao Pearl?

160
00:07:02,959 --> 00:07:05,120
From the moment I got this Lingxiao Pearl

161
00:07:05,279 --> 00:07:06,759
until we walked out of the tree,

162
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:09,439
I had already walked this entire path once.

163
00:07:15,079 --> 00:07:16,040
Are you serious?

164
00:07:16,959 --> 00:07:18,639
Didn't you say I had opened my third eye

165
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,639
Weren't you curious why I didn't turn around

166
00:07:20,639 --> 00:07:22,720
and knew your foot would sink into the tree sap?

167
00:07:24,639 --> 00:07:26,759
I also knew when this ground crack would split open.

168
00:07:28,519 --> 00:07:31,160
I've already been through all of this once.

169
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:38,079
So, whatever we're about to say,

170
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,120
you already know in advance.

171
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:43,639
I just can't be sure

172
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:46,680
whether all this is real or a premonition.

173
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:56,000
So it seems

174
00:07:56,279 --> 00:07:57,480
the function of the Lingxiao Pearl

175
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,480
isn't to help people Become immortal,

176
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,959
but to cause one's consciousness to travel.

177
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:03,519
Then...

178
00:08:04,199 --> 00:08:06,680
what does this have to do with Dawei?

179
00:08:09,439 --> 00:08:11,240
Want to know what he did to you?

180
00:08:11,839 --> 00:08:12,399
Me?

181
00:08:12,759 --> 00:08:14,040
What could this kid possibly do?

182
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:16,959
He wouldn't push all three of us into the lava, right?

183
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,040
Who did he push?

184
00:08:23,959 --> 00:08:24,800
The three of you.

185
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:26,199
He even pushed me in.

186
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:28,199
What were you trying to get?

187
00:08:29,399 --> 00:08:30,240
The Lingxiao Pearl?

188
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:32,039
He doesn't even have a curse.

189
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:34,120
What would you want it for?

190
00:08:34,399 --> 00:08:35,559
Because our friend Ding Dawei

191
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:36,960
is in cahoots with Bai Lingling.

192
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,279
They work for the same boss.

193
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,519
They want to use us

194
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:43,240
to find the Lingxiao Pearl, right?

195
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,759
Is what Old Chen said true?

196
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,399
Of course it isn't.

197
00:08:46,639 --> 00:08:47,519
I think, Bro,

198
00:08:47,519 --> 00:08:49,919
touching the Pearl messed with your mind.

199
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:52,440
The one you should be worried about right now isn't me. It's him.

200
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,159
Shut up!

201
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:56,200
Fatty's gonna ask you one question.

202
00:08:57,159 --> 00:08:58,559
Do you know Bai Lingling or not?

203
00:08:58,559 --> 00:08:59,440
I don't.

204
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,559
Fatty,

205
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:03,600
you've been suspicious of me the whole way.

206
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:05,279
We've been through so much together.

207
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:08,080
Don't you know what kind of person I am?

208
00:09:08,799 --> 00:09:10,399
How can you doubt my character

209
00:09:10,399 --> 00:09:11,840
based on one thing Bro said?

210
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:16,720
Ding Dawei, we really don't know you.

211
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:20,000
We know nothing about your past.

212
00:09:20,519 --> 00:09:21,799
And the reason you came here,

213
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,360
we know even less about.

214
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,559
You suspect me too?

215
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:25,799
Just because

216
00:09:25,799 --> 00:09:27,200
he says he saw me kill you?

217
00:09:27,519 --> 00:09:28,919
That was just his hallucination.

218
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,080
Aren't you afraid

219
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,840
he'll take the Lingxiao Pearl for himself?

220
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,519
You may not realize this,

221
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,440
but among all of us,

222
00:09:36,919 --> 00:09:38,799
the one who cares least about the Pearl

223
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,480
is Chen Youxi.

224
00:09:41,679 --> 00:09:42,480
Bro,

225
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:45,080
didn't you see the photo of me and my dad?

226
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,559
What's there to doubt?

227
00:09:52,039 --> 00:09:53,879
How do you know I saw the photo?

228
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:58,159
My father spent his whole life searching

229
00:09:58,159 --> 00:09:59,480
for the Kashenfu Ghost Beauty Butterfly.

230
00:10:00,679 --> 00:10:02,159
I want to fulfill his last wish.

231
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:08,840
Dawei,

232
00:10:17,759 --> 00:10:19,720
so this really was your setup, huh?

233
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:26,159
Fine, just great.

234
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:28,639
And here I thought

235
00:10:29,279 --> 00:10:31,080
I'd made some true friends.

236
00:10:31,679 --> 00:10:32,559
Turns out

237
00:10:33,679 --> 00:10:35,279
it was all for nothing in the end.

238
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,279
In that case,

239
00:10:38,679 --> 00:10:40,399
no need to talk about friendship.

240
00:10:42,519 --> 00:10:43,639
This Lingxiao Pearl,

241
00:10:46,879 --> 00:10:47,840
I'm taking it.

242
00:10:48,039 --> 00:10:48,840
Take it, my ass!

243
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:50,080
Fatty's coming over to deal with you!

244
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:53,320
Run back, head up!

245
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:03,600
Looking for this?

246
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:09,759
Stay behind me.

247
00:11:31,039 --> 00:11:31,600
No way.

248
00:11:31,879 --> 00:11:33,960
I gotta find a way over to help Old Chen.

249
00:11:34,799 --> 00:11:35,440
Wait.

250
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:38,000
Going now will just add weight to the ground.

251
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:39,320
You'll fall down together.

252
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,480
What do we do?

253
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:58,600
Old Chen!

254
00:12:22,799 --> 00:12:23,320
Bro,

255
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:26,799
Just let me go.

256
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:31,840
There's no point in me living anymore.

257
00:12:34,559 --> 00:12:35,879
And in your eyes,

258
00:12:36,639 --> 00:12:40,200
someone like me doesn't deserve to live.

259
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:45,000
Dawei, it's okay to be selfish,

260
00:12:45,559 --> 00:12:46,840
but you can't be ruthless.

261
00:12:49,159 --> 00:12:50,679
What do you know?

262
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:56,080
I was raised by the organization as a machine

263
00:12:57,759 --> 00:12:59,440
just to find the Lingxiao Pearl.

264
00:13:02,519 --> 00:13:03,799
I only learned how to deceive,

265
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:06,960
never how to be a person.

266
00:13:11,679 --> 00:13:14,559
Sometimes, I really envy you.

267
00:13:15,399 --> 00:13:16,600
At least you have

268
00:13:17,879 --> 00:13:19,320
people around you who truly care.

269
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:21,519
The days I spent with you all

270
00:13:22,639 --> 00:13:25,240
were the most thrilling,

271
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,200
most exciting,

272
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:29,159
and the happiest,

273
00:13:30,279 --> 00:13:31,600
warmest days of my life.

274
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:33,919
That's the truth.

275
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:37,919
I'm not lying to you.

276
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:38,679
Dawei!

277
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:40,559
Dawei!

278
00:13:50,159 --> 00:13:51,759
Old Chen, forget about him!

279
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:52,559
Get over here!

280
00:13:52,799 --> 00:13:54,559
Hurry, the volcano's about to erupt!

281
00:13:55,159 --> 00:13:56,720
The volcano's erupting!

282
00:14:20,240 --> 00:14:21,559
Old Chen, be careful!

283
00:14:22,799 --> 00:14:24,240
The rope's about to burn through!

284
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:25,200
Grab my leg!

285
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:33,559
Old Chen,

286
00:14:38,120 --> 00:14:38,720
are you okay?

287
00:14:39,279 --> 00:14:39,759
I'm fine.

288
00:14:40,799 --> 00:14:41,720
That was close.

289
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:43,840
Such a shame about the Lingxiao Pearl.

290
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:45,080
Nothing to be sorry about.

291
00:14:45,399 --> 00:14:46,840
It can't break my curse anyway.

292
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:48,519
Let's hurry up before the volcano erupts

293
00:14:48,519 --> 00:14:49,039
and get out of here!

294
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:51,639
Move, move!

295
00:14:51,639 --> 00:14:52,960
Go, hurry, go!

296
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:17,480
Look at that.

297
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:21,720
I gotta say, it's pretty spectacular.

298
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:23,440
Just like a giant sparkler.

299
00:15:24,399 --> 00:15:26,080
What a dramatic change.

300
00:15:26,879 --> 00:15:28,200
The Dian King's dream to Become immortal

301
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:30,039
was just a misunderstanding.

302
00:15:31,519 --> 00:15:33,480
Whether he misunderstood or not isn't our business.

303
00:15:33,919 --> 00:15:35,720
The point is, we got it pretty wrong ourselves.

304
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:37,039
Another wasted trip.

305
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:39,159
Chen Youxi,

306
00:15:39,919 --> 00:15:42,360
for the Lingxiao Pearl to have such an impact

307
00:15:42,480 --> 00:15:44,399
and stimulation on your consciousness,

308
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:46,600
that doesn't seem like Earth civilization.

309
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:48,399
I think it's just the human brain

310
00:15:48,399 --> 00:15:49,960
operating at high speed,

311
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:52,879
predicting all the possibilities.

312
00:15:54,279 --> 00:15:55,919
It's just that my deductions

313
00:15:55,919 --> 00:15:57,240
are a little more advanced,

314
00:15:57,759 --> 00:15:59,080
a little more accurate,

315
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:00,519
a little clearer,

316
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:01,799
a little more refined.

317
00:16:02,480 --> 00:16:05,200
And his ego? More than a little inflated.

318
00:16:05,879 --> 00:16:07,600
Let's get a little farther away from him.

319
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:09,320
This Earth can barely contain him.

320
00:16:09,879 --> 00:16:11,200
Let's go, let's go.

321
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:11,879
Move.

322
00:16:17,039 --> 00:16:18,000
Hey, Old Chen,

323
00:16:18,440 --> 00:16:19,759
If you've got this skill,

324
00:16:20,039 --> 00:16:21,519
I'll invite you to play cards next time.

325
00:16:21,639 --> 00:16:23,039
Maybe we'd actually win.

326
00:16:23,399 --> 00:16:24,559
That skill of his,

327
00:16:24,919 --> 00:16:26,960
who knows if it can be sustained.

328
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:29,120
No worries. When it runs out,

329
00:16:29,120 --> 00:16:30,879
we'll have him touch a live wire to recharge.

330
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:02,840
The Lingxiao Pearl isn't with them.

